Titanium Mobile 1.7.0 - 06/06/2011
==================================

This release candidate includes general bug fixes for Android and iPhone.
Please see the updated [Titanium Mobile Reference Documentation for 1.7.0](/apidoc/mobile/1.7.0) 

[Full list of Issues that were addressed in 1.7.0](http://jira.appcelerator.org/secure/IssueNavigator.jspa?mode=hide&requestId=10188) 

New Features on iOS and Android
-------------------------------

- [Buffer and Codec](http://developer.appcelerator.com/blog/2011/04/titanium-mobile-intro-series-buffer-and-codec.html)
- [Streams](http://developer.appcelerator.com/blog/2011/05/titanium-mobile-intro-series-streams.html)
- [Sockets](http://developer.appcelerator.com/blog/2011/05/titanium-mobile-intro-series-sockets.html)
- Typed return values from ResultSets [Android TIMOB-3519](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-3519) and [iOS TIMOB-3393](http://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TIMOB-3393)
- Improved debugger integration

